                                    </div>
                                    <br>
                                    <p>A Cub Jamboree is to be held at our Lochgoilhead National Activity Centre this summer. The five-day camp will be held from 17 July and will be open to both groups and individual Cubs. Lochgoilhead has hosted many popular Cubs events, including successful Cubs centenary events this year. “The huge range of adventurous activities on offer at Lochgoilhead makes it the perfect venue for keeping active young minds fully engaged.” Said Head of National Activity Centres, Graeme Young. “Indoor accommodation and all catering is included the package at Lochgoilhead so that Leaders can focus on making sure their young people can have a real adventure.” Full details, including cost and booking, will be made available soon so look out for news on our website and social media channels.</p>
